        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Keep Student Veterans in Their Homes Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes <horizes> the Department of Veterans Affairs to continue to pay educational assistance and subsistence allowances to eligible veterans and eligible persons enrolled in specified courses solely for a monthly housing stipend of up to four months following a permanent school closure.</horizes></p> <p>A housing or educational assistance payment shall not be counted against the aggregate period for which such assistance may be provided or charged against the individual's entitlement to educational assistance.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2017-05-25</actionDate>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-06-17T12:32:47Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
